da fun ... if I had all the time in the world :P<br /><br />Anyway, I was saying that I'm <em>personally</em> not concerned with running an NES emulator on a GBA, not that I wasn't interested in the GB itself.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">I'll take the rest of this up privately, because actually after reading some of your responses, I'm pretty damn pissed off.</div>
